<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP10">
<l>koṇṭal vaṇṇaṉaik kōvala ṉāyveṇṇe</l>
<l>yuṇṭa vāyaṉeṉ ṉuḷḷaṅ kavarntāṉai</l>
<l>yaṇṭar kōṉaṇi yaraṅkaṉeṉ ṉamutiṉaik</l>
<l>kaṇṭa kaṇkaṇmaṟ ṟoṉṟiṉaik kāṇāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My eyes that have seen the Nectar—Him from the ornate Raṅgam,</l>
<l>the King of celestials, Him who stole my heart,</l>
<l>Him whose mouth ate butter as a Cowherd,</l>
<l>the cloud-hued [Lord]—shall not see another thing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
